	<ThingDef ParentName="BaseHumanMakeableGun">
		<defName>EOTF_RetroRifle</defName>
		<label>Retro Rifle</label>
		<description>Nostalgia is a hell of a thing. People appreciate a classic or at least the idea of a classic, so many companies put our various “retro” themed weaponry. The “Retro” Weapon market leads to many interesting designs that feel old but are in fact very new. This model being built of a famous weapon used centuries ago during humanity’s Dark Age. Though not a direct copy this imitation still sells well enough and maintains enough aspects of the original that many don’t notice the difference. Often found in the hands of the middle-class mercenary or with people who assumed this would be more useful than a classic car on the Rim.\n\n Millenia Model 0 "The Classica."</description>
		<graphicData>
			<graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>
			<texPath>Things/Item/Equipment/WeaponRanged/RetroRifle</texPath>
		</graphicData>
		<soundInteract>Interact_Rifle</soundInteract>
