	<ThingDef ParentName="BaseHumanMakeableGun">
		<defName>EOTF_Hyperblaster</defName>
		<label>Hyperblaster</label>
		<description>A relatively new weapon in comparison to many of its compatriots on the Rim. The Hyperblaster was one of the first charge weapons created during the Human-Mechanoid Wars and it shows. Heavy, clumsy, but packs more wallop than modern Charge weapons due to its very unrefined abilities. These traits are the reason it is called the Hyperblaster rather than its official name or even the other names given to it like Siegebreaker and Quakemaker. Though being replaced by more convenient Charge weapons, the weapon is still in production and will likely continue to do so, because it works, and it works well especially when you have power armored soldiers who can easily carry it.\n\nOfficial Name: Camlann Varangian V.II.</description>
