		<label>Service Rifle (Bayonet)</label>
		<description>Once considered the right arm of the free worlds, the partisan Rifle emerged during the great schisms. Before the mechanoid threat, separatists groups armed themselves with this ancient design. After centuries of fighting the Domain, the Bugs, and the Bots, the design has been further streamlined. parts made with polymers or woods changes to shaped steel, fine crafted metal turned to mass production stamps, and quality turned to quantity. Despite this. it is a favorite among mercenaries and colonial militias, some groups have even modified them to take bayonets and other ancient modifications. Now the weapon represents the worlds striving for freedom.\n\nOfficial Name: Armex-Armalite Free License.</description>
