	<ThingDef ParentName="BaseHumanMakeableGun">
		<defName>EOTF_DominionRifle</defName>
		<label>domionion rifle</label>
		<description>Based on an ancient design from humanities past, this rifle was recently designed on the world of Sisu. Sisu is a fortressworld on the very edge of the Coreworlds, it is here where the longest single war in human history has occured, the War of Sisu, which has raged for 1,371 years. The world has fought not against the mechanoids or insectoids, but against the Black King, a rogue AI which used an army of clones made for the conquest of the stars during the Great Domain Era. The Black King has ground his forces against the Sisunians for centuries with few gains. This rifle was designed to fight humans who lack armor and in this aspect it functions very well, shredding flesh with ease. The design has been exported throughout the Rimworlds, with many adopting them for defensive weapons.\n\nOfficial Name: Terys-Gua R4 "Shredder."</description>
